Installation Instructions
=========================

NOTE: stratagus ( http://stratagus.org ) is required.
wargus and stratagus version must match
(same version or svn from the same date)

The Battle.Net version is NOT supported, you must use the DOS version.

Either the Expansion or Original CD can be used.
Do not extract from both. Extract from one CD only.

1. extract data: './build.sh -p /path/to/cd [ -o /path/to/outputdir ]'
	eg:
	./build.sh -p d:/
	./build.sh -p /cdrom

2. start stratagus: '/path/to/stratagus -d /path/to/outputdir'
	eg:	
	./stratagus -d data.wc2
